## Claude-specific notes

- Skills live in `.claude/skills/`; load them by trigger, not preemptively.
- Slash commands live in `.claude/commands/` (incl. `/aiws-doc-sync`<% if (it.sdd.enabled) { %> and `/aiws-sdd-*`<% } %>).
- MCP servers are configured in `.mcp.json`<% if (it.mcp.includes("context7")) { %> (includes **context7** for up-to-date library docs)<% } %>.
- Local-only overrides go in `.claude/settings.local.json` (git-ignored).
